body.paragraph:
 ‘‘Ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, kālakiriyā bahuno janassa anutappāānutappā 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='5', original='ānutappā (sī.)', type='auto', previous=' Ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, kālakiriyā bahuno janassa anutappā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='anutappā'}
	Alternative{lang='sī.', text='ānutappā'}}
hoti. Katamassa ekapuggalassa? Tathāgatassa arahato sammāsambuddhassa. Imassa kho, bhikkhave, ekapuggalassa kālakiriyā bahuno janassa anutappā hotī’’ti.
